-- Clal Industries Rises to 3-Week High on Access Sale Completion
-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 2012-07-08T12:09:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-08/clal-industries-rises-to-3-week-high-on-access-sale-completion.html
Clal Industries and Investments Ltd. 
advanced to the highest in almost three weeks after IDB
Development Corp. said it completed the sale of a stake in the
 investment company  to Access Industries Holdings Inc.  The shares of Tel Aviv-based Clal  increased  4.2 percent to
12.57 shekels, the highest on a closing basis since June 18, at
2:56 p.m. in  Tel Aviv .  IDB Holding Corp. (IDBH) , which has an 86.83
percent stake in IDB Development according to data compiled by
Bloomberg, gained 3.1 percent to 13.40 shekels.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shoshanna Solomon in Tel Aviv at 
 ssolomon22@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
